verbose_text: Future work by our group will involve, for example, measurements of the triplet levels of the sensitizers, using Gd complex analogues, to assess the impact of making the complexes more asymmetric on the modulation of the energy transfer between the ligand triplet state and the excited Eu accepting level (5 D 1 or 5 D 0), a key intramolecular energy transfer step.
